data.description: Make this 2 story house your home!  Located in Westin Hills West, this modern farmhouse updated home is perfect for your family!  Enjoy your fully fenced in back yard with a sprinkler system and kids play set.  Close to Standing Bear Lake, schools, shopping, parks and trails.  Beautiful remodeled kitchen features butcher block countertops, shiplap island, KitchenAid double oven induction range and dishwasher. Updated fireplace & light fixtures, new LVT flooring throughout the main level plus areas upstairs.  Carpet is just a year old and has been professionally cleaned.  Recent spray foam insulation upgrades in attic, garage, and basement for better efficiency and comfort. Unfinished basement features high ceilings and an egress window, so this could easily be finished for extra space.  Agent is related to seller and has equity.
